STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Barrington G. MCDONALD, Defendant-Movant. M-436/437/438 September Term 2017
079683 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 8, 2017

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motions for relaxation of the Court Rules on copying requirements (M-436), and to file a reply brief (M-438) are granted; and it is further.

ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal (M-437) is denied.
